cdata.name: EduCoin
cdata.desc:
EduCoin isa Blockchain-based education platform. It provides users with access to educational content on a global scale, at the same time that rewards with the native platforms tokens(EDU) the ones who published it. EduCoinworks through a P2P (Peer to Peer) matching mechanism, using A.I. to find the appropriate teacher to a specific student need.

The EDU token is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency developed by EduCoin. It will power the platform as it willserve topay for educational content transactions made by the users on the platform.
